WARNING: Problem with directory [/home/stash/${stash.home}/lib], exists: [false], isDirectory: [false], canRead: [false]
Killing Tomcat with the PID: 1728
{code}

However, the directory _does_ exist:

{code}
$ ls -lad  ~stash/lib/
drwxr-xr-x 2 stash stash 4096 Jul 24 14:30 /home/stash/lib/
{code}

